{"tid":922628,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"拳王休戰逾年後表演賽即勝　曹星如宣布復出爭入東京奧運","createTime":"2018-11-30T14:08:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-30T15:32:16.000Z","uid":20933,"like":3,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ce5e7cd179e71076b64a172e4b9df7605f640199","tid":922628,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T14:08:55.000Z","msg":"港人苦等13個月，終於等到拳王復出，卻是一個不一樣的回歸。港產「神奇小子」曹星如今晚重返擂台，與中華台北業餘拳手合演表演賽，在陣陣「星如加油」的打氣聲中，復出首擊即力戰而勝。賽後他更即席宣布，將重返業餘拳壇，爭取重燃10年前的奧運夢。<br />\n<br />\n在灣仔修頓室內場館約2000名拳迷入場見證下，職業生涯錄得22連勝的曹星如（Rex）克服眼傷，在3回合各3分鐘的業餘擂台表演賽，迎戰中華台北21歲小將江奕宏。儘管因眼部重創休養多時，但Rex在3回合全程佔上風，多番施展組合拳擊中對手。曹星如雖已31歲，但今次對陣年輕對手時，在3回合賽事中體能都不受影響，最終獲拳證一致裁定取勝。<br />\n<br />\n自去年10月擊敗日本拳手河野公平，Rex因眼部重創休息1整年，其間失掉兩條洲際金腰帶。今次他在「Ultimate Extreme Fight」表演賽復出，轉戰業餘拳壇為復出鋪路，賽後更帶淚說：「我離開擂台一整年了，多謝大家依然支持我。記得10年前，自己在奧運外圍賽第一圈就被淘汰，當時怪責自己沒用，今次希望在2020年東京奧運，可以爭取資格。無論成功與否，我都會盡全力，希望大家繼續支持我，裝備自己迎戰來年資格賽。」"},{"pid":"3403ea46e0ae9ffde9eafb06c39edc052f8d0bc4","tid":922628,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T14:09:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20181130/s00006/1543586313362\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20181130%2Fs00006%2F1543586313362&d=F58BbF%2FyGUkumBGUeky%2FTQEk2Noh57F05xbgvjQdsX8%3D&h=53c71e4b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20181130%2Fs00006%2F1543586313362&h=70a59faf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20181130/s00006/1543586313362</a>"},{"pid":"8ebbf2e77e13445cbd6c1d762f3b79dbccc33f59","tid":922628,"uid":90304,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T14:09:48.000Z","msg":"洗哂d 錢又出返黎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"004e7e0b31cd6fbc9da750d1c54080e1535bd4ad","tid":922628,"uid":29270,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"8ebbf2e77e13445cbd6c1d762f3b79dbccc33f59","tid":922628,"uid":90304,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T14:09:48.000Z","msg":"洗哂d 錢又出返黎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T14:11:11.000Z","msg":"自去年10月擊敗日本拳手河野公平，Rex因眼部重創休息1整年"},{"pid":"8e8a2ce913f3987578d8310c7357fbffcb5b7958","tid":922628,"uid":1823,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T14:12:05.000Z","msg":"打業餘拳手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6bf86787eaf263ffe201129d7171b894e9be204","tid":922628,"uid":211461,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T14:23:56.000Z","msg":"如意算盤：<br />\n借奧運之名 暗退職業拳壇<br />\n2020就話都33-4歲 打唔返職業啦<br />\n咁神奇小子曹星如22連勝就會萬世流芳<br />\n成為香港傳奇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcfbb2625ef0d988c54470597551a21aa07621d3","tid":922628,"uid":90304,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T15:32:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gE1WyFo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgE1WyFo.png&h=11876f93&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}